## 🛠️ Repository Structure

```text
├── dataset/               # Scripts for CIFAR-10 download and preprocessing
├── models/
│   ├── unet.py            # U-Net architecture with Time Embeddings & Attention
│   └── diffusion.py       # Forward/Reverse diffusion process logic
├── train.py               # Training loop and loss optimization
├── denoise_eval.py        # Evaluation script for inference and noise removal
├── requirements.txt       # Dependencies
└── README.md              # Project documentation
